Daisy Aitkens https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daisy_Aitkens 0 Daisy Aitkens (Born 25 March 1986) is an English actress, writer and director who is best known for her roles in the TV series Fear, Stress and Anger and Watson and Oliver. In addition, she was responsible for writing and directing the 2015 film 96 Ways To Say I Love You.
